(18122, 24, 'matching', 'Students\' self-perception is a more effective driver of self-confidence than actual achievement is.', '["medical practitoners","specialised tasks","available resources","reduced illness","professional authority","technology experts"]', 'available resources', NULL, 'AI currently has a limited role in the way [match]24[/match] are allocated in the health service. The positive aspect of AI having a bigger role is that it would be more efficient and lead to patient benefits. However, such a change would result, for example, in certain [match]25[/match] not having their current level of  [match]26[/match].  It is therefore important that AI goals are appropriate so that discriminatory practices could be avoided.', 1, NULL, NOW());
