(18133, 31, 'matching', 'According to Professor John Hattie of the Melbourne Education Research Institute, there is very little indication that streaming leads to ______. He points out that, in schools which use streaming, the most significant impact is on those students placed in the ______, especially where a large proportion of them have ______. Meanwhile, for the ______, there appears to be only minimal advantage. A further issue is that teachers tend to have ______ of students in streamed groups.', '["wrong classes","lower expectations","average learners","bottom sets","brightest pupils","disadvantaged backgrounds","weaker students","higher achievements","positive impressions"]', 'differentiation', NULL, 'According to Professor John Hattie of the Melbourne Education Research Institute, there is very little indication that streaming leads to [match]31[/match]. He points out that, in schools which use streaming, the most significant impact is on those students placed in the [match]32[/match], especially where a large proportion of them have [match]33[/match]. Meanwhile, for the [match]34[/match], there appears to be only minimal advantage. A further issue is that teachers tend to have [match]35[/match] of students in streamed groups.', 1, NULL, NOW());
